<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.4.1">
<l>kaṇcōra veṅkuruti vantiḻiya ventaḻalpōl kūnta lāḷai</l>
<l>maṇcēra mulaiyuṇṭa māmatalāy vāṉavartaṅ kōvē yeṉṟu</l>
<l>viṇcēru miḷantiṅka ḷakaṭuriñcu maṇimāṭa malku celvat</l>
<l>taṇcēṟai yemperumāṉ tāḷtoḻuvār kāṇmiṉeṉ talaimē lārē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who worship at the feet of our great lord of cool Cēṟai</l>
<l rend="indent">of abundant wealth,</l>
<l>With beautiful mansions which rub the belly of the young moon in the sky,</l>
<l>Praying, “King of the celestials, very [young] baby who ate from the breast</l>
<l rend="indent">of the one with long hair like blazing fire,</l>
<l>So she crashed to earth as her eyes oozed [tears] as hot blood flowed down,”</l>
<l rend="indent">	see, they are on my head.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
